<br>
Best for the SK first, then move to the shammy.<br>
<br>
First snare the sk, and then immediately cast sunbeam. The trolls will run towards the ogre vendors there when sunbeamed, EVERY time.  Then you have your group nuke the fire outta them, when sunbeam breaks you should have it low enough that the tanks can intercept it on the way back, and finish it off while you med.<br>
<br>
The respawn rate on the trolls makes this a VERY viable strategy, and if you fizzle or a resist hits, you still have the time to engage or back up and recast.<br>
